net.java.jddac.jmdi.comm
Class WrapperCoder

java.lang.Object
  net.java.jddac.jmdi.comm.WrapperCoder
All Implemented Interfaces:
ByteCoder
public class WrapperCoder
extends java.lang.Object
implements ByteCoder

A ByteCoder that handles HTTP multipart forms. On decode, it assumes there will be only one part and it will be named 'xml'. Likewise, on encode it generates only one part named 'xml'.
